<%- include('partials/head', { pageTitle: pageTitle || 'Editorial Team' }) %>
<%- include('partials/header', { categories }) %>
      <section class="info-page">
        <div class="container">
          <h1>Tech Industry News Editorial Team</h1>
          <p class="lead">
            Our editorial desk blends experience across business reporting, data analysis, and cybersecurity research to ensure every story we publish is accurate, contextual, and useful for modern operators.
          </p>
          <div class="info-grid">
            <section class="info-section">
              <h2>Collective Expertise</h2>
              <p>
                The team monitors AI labs, semiconductor supply chains, enterprise software vendors, and security teams day and night. We track major product roadmaps, funding moves, and policy updates so you can grasp what matters without pausing your build.
              </p>
              <ul>
                <li>Daily monitoring of lab blogs, regulatory filings, supply-chain alerts, and investor calls.</li>
                <li>Hands-on familiarity with cloud platforms, AI tooling, and enterprise procurement cycles.</li>
                <li>Experience translating dense technical research into actionable context.</li>
              </ul>
            </section>
            <section class="info-section">
              <h2>Editorial Workflow</h2>
              <p>
                Every article goes through ideation, fact gathering, rewriting, and peer review. Automated tools surface leads, but final copy only ships after human editors verify numbers, add background, and align tone with our guidelines.
              </p>
              <ul>
                <li>Primary source validation and citation review.</li>
                <li>Headline and deck shaping to emphasize reader takeaways.</li>
                <li>Copy editing for clarity, neutrality, and consistency.</li>
              </ul>
            </section>
            <section class="info-section">
              <h2>Reader Commitments</h2>
              <p>
                We publish corrections promptly, flag updates when stories evolve, and avoid speculation unless clearly labelled. Feedback from readers informs future coverage priorities and helps us refine the format of daily summaries.
              </p>
              <p>
                If you spot a detail we should update, contact the team through our <a href="/contact">contact page</a>. We review every request within two business days.
              </p>
            </section>
            <section class="info-section">
              <h2>Coverage Principles</h2>
              <ul>
                <li>Focus on verifiable facts and reproducible data.</li>
                <li>Highlight impact on engineers, security leads, product owners, and policy teams.</li>
                <li>Give emerging builders and regions visibility alongside the largest vendors.</li>
              </ul>
            </section>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
